title: Ep 2629 - Jethalaal on Crossroads
shortDesc: Surma's move of cancelling the deal with Baga and Nattu Kaka has put Jethalal in a very bad position. What will Jethalal do now?

title: Ep 2630 - Nattu and Bagas Secret Plan
shortDesc: After Surma breaks the news of deal of Gada Electronics being cancelled by Baga and Nattu, Jethalal is furious with them and scolds them. But suddenly there's a twist in the story. Will the fate of Jethalal change?

title: Ep 2631 - The Super Hit Plan
shortDesc: Surma Bhai is surprised at the clever plan executed by Baga and Nattu Kaka. Popatlal too has played an integral part in the plan. Jethalal is overjoyed as his worries are over and he gets back the keys to Gada Electronics.

title: Ep 2632 - Preparations for New Year
shortDesc: Taarak and Anjali reminisce what has happened in Gokuldhaam in 2018. Bhide is worried about the new year celebrations and decorations but Tapu sena has taken over the task as usual and have already started with the preparations.

title: Ep 2633 - New Year Surprise
shortDesc: Everyone is set and ready to enjoy the new year celebrations in Gokuldham society with their college look theme but before the celebratrions begin it is interrupted by Inspector Pandey who alleges that there's stolen gold in the society. Who is respo

title: Ep 2634 - New Year Bash
shortDesc: After a lot of illegal gold is found in the houses of Gokuldham members, Inspector Chalu Pandey informs that a new police office is out to investigate the matter whose name is Inscpector Bhalerao. Stay tuned to find out what happens next!

title: Ep 2635 - Ranveer Singhs Surprise
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members finally learn that Bhalerao is none other than Ranveer Singh. The society members are relieved and overjoyed at the same time realizing that Ranveer Singh has paid a surprise visit to Gokuldham.

title: Ep 2636 - Taaraks New Year Resolution
shortDesc: After welcoming Ranveer Singh and the new year, Gokuldham calls it a night. The next morning things change as Taarak has decided to follow a strict dieting plan which shocks Anjali. How long will the resolution go on for. Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2637 - New Year Resolution in Danger
shortDesc: All of the male members have decided to take Taarak on a lavish breakfast as a new year gift.  How will Taarak come out of this situation? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2638 - The Cheat Meal
shortDesc: Taarak is reluctant to taste the variety of foods on offer. While Jethalal and others enjoy the foods they have ordered, Taarak is left disappointed. Finally, Taarak decides to have a go at the tasty treats and forget for a moment about Anjali.

title: Ep 2639 - Panic Mode
shortDesc: Taarak is panicking as he thinks that Anjali will be heart broken if she get's to know about the truth of him breaking his resolution from photogram. Will he be able to avoid the situation?

title: Ep 2640 - Sigh of Relief
shortDesc: Tapu and Goli somehow manage to handle the situation until the arrival of Taarak and gang. Taarak on seeing Anjali using photogram visualises his doom. Will he come out of the situation unharmed? Stay tuned!

title: Ep 2641 - The Showdown
shortDesc: Taarak decides to confess to Anjali that he broke his resolution. Everyone tries to stop him from doing so. But Taarak couldn't control and blurts out the truth infront of Anjali. What will be Anjali's reaction? Stay Tuned!

title: Ep 2642 - A Review of 2018
shortDesc: The men gang of Gokuldham sit at Abdul's shop and discuss what happened in 2018 and what are they expecting of 2019. Bhide gives a test of being husband. How will it turn out for Bhide? Stay Tuned!

title: Ep 2643 - Jethalals Surprise
shortDesc: Sankranti is around the corner and the Gokuldham society members are ecstatic to celebrate it with fervor.  Jethalal has decided to surprise the society members during this kite flying season. What surprises has Jethalal planned?
